channel.title: 508 SystemServer 508 1ste post
channel.description:
Ok, before I begin, just so theres no complaints, this WAS a Bulby source, so SOME credit to him. However, I have edited a LOT, so Id probably make it like this: Bulby 50%, Me 40%, itemdb.co.nr 5%, Moparscape.org/smf 5%.
http://uppit.com/v/NXUL58Y4
New Link. Sorry For Fold Link. :|
Here are a few things:
All 24 skills work!!! (Includes Summoning, Construction, and Hunter!) (NEW means it wasnt in the Bulby base)
-STAFF ZONE ON GE ROOF! NEW -All 24 skill-cape emotes work 100%!!! -All 24 Skills work and level! -Clan Chat -Get third age by winning in fight pits! -Real Castle Wars & Clan Wars! -Perfect Dueling!! -Fight pits!!! -Dragon Slayer -Jad drops FCape!! NEW -Pets follow you! -Admin Pets! NEW -Summoning NPCS Follow you! -ALL NEW GWD WITH KILLCOUNT NEVER BEFORE SEEN IN BULBY BASE!!! (PICS SOON) NEW -GWD Bosses drop hilts and godsword blades! NEW -Use a hilt with blade to get a godsword! NEW -All GS specs work! -All Barrows Specs Work! -Wildy Levels Work! NEW
ADMIN COMMANDS
::staff - teles to staff zone NEW ::pnpc #### -changes you into a monster (npc) NEW ::unpc -changes you back to normal NEW ::mute #### -mutes a player(####) NEW ::unmute #### -obvious... NEW ::kick #### -dcs the person for a second ::master - all 99's ::slave - all 98's ::capes2 -gives all skillcapes into your invintory (DONT FORGET THE 2!) ::hoods -all skillcape hoods ::bh -teleport to bounty hunter ::cw - tele to castle wars ::range -gives a whip ::food -full invintory of monkfish ::pouches -gives one of every pouch ::fullkc -kives a killcount of 200 for every GWD boss area.. (do ::gwd to get there) NEW ::emote #### -does the emote number.... there are like 500 ::gfx #### -does a special effect... there are like thousands of these.. ::npc ### -spawns a certain npc.. over 10k of these.. ::tele @@@@ #### $ -teles to a specific location (@@@@ = x, #### = y, $ = height of location ::god -kool special effect an makes u fly NEW ::godoff -turns god off NEW ::coords -gets you coords... ex : X = 4353, Y = 3123 ::teletome #### -teleport the person to you ::private -teles you to a private place NEW ::teleto #### -teles you to specific person ::di NAME ITEMID ITEMAMT - Deletes a certain number(itemamt) of a specific item(itemid) from a specific persons invintory(name). NEW!!! ~~NEVER BEFORE SEEN IN ANY PRIVATE SERVER~~ ::rs - Fills the special energy bar (restore special) NEW
NORMAL COMMANDS
::kc - see your killcount of each god in the GWD NEW ::suggestion BLAHBLAH - Gives me a suggestion to add to server (blahblah is the suggestion) ::reportbug BLAHBLAH- report a game buh ::reportabuse NAME REASON- report someone breaking the rules ::wildy - tele to wildy for pking ::gwd - tele to godwars NEW ::fixgwd - if u go underground in the god wars dungeon, use this to go back up NEW ::pm NAME MESSAGE_LIKE_THIS - private message someone. There name is NAME, and you message needs to have _ instead of spaces. Like this ::pm david Hey_whats_up!_Want_to_talk? NEW ::goinhouse NAME - go inside someones house ::whereis NAME - find out where someone is ::savebackup - save a backup incase u get reset. DO THIS EVERY TIME U LOG OUT! ::loadbackup - loads a backup. ONLY IF U SAVED ONE! ::yell MESSAGE - makes a message everyone can hear ::newroom - in construction, makes a new room ::deleteroom - easy.. ::help - see a few commands ::home - teles home to the GE ::players - see whos online ::char - change your character male/female NEW
I'm deciding whether to show a link or not... please say if you would like it. I might add the link.
Greetz Dominique.
